Photographs are an important part of the description so study them carefully. All items, new or used, may, at times, have a tiny flaw if you look closely enough. I describe items as accurately as I can, pointing out anything I see as a flaw but on occasion, I may miss something small. This is not a reason for calling an item "not as described". Not liking the way an item of clothing looks on you is not an acceptable reason for return. "Doesn't fit" is also NOT a reason for return; that's why we stress the need to measure a similar garment to ensure fit. COLOR: Another issue could be that of the item’s color. One person’s "gold" may be another person’s "yellow" so don’t rely on the words alone – ask specific questions, and study the photographs. Also, the photo does not always reflect the exact color of the item. The color you see depends on the camera, the lighting and your computer monitor. If the photo does not reflect the color accurately I mention this in the description, but again, please ask questions. SIZES: With clothing and shoes, if you have not measured an item of yours to compare with my measurements and the item does not fit, this is not a reason for return. Do not go by the marked size alone as some used items may have been taken in or let out and all designers have different ways of sizing CONDITION: Please do not expect absolute perfection in vintage items as they will all show some signs of wear. Please look at my definitions for vintage: Excellent – I have checked the item carefully and found no obvious flaws. If applied to vintage it may show tiny signs of wear that have no effect on the beauty of the piece. Again ask questions. Very Good – Means there may be a few small but practically unnoticeable flaws. No items will be listed that are not in new, excellent or very good condition except pieces that are listed as repair pieces SHIPPING COSTS We always pack items to ensure their safety. Arrival time for international items greatly depends on the destination country’s Customs procedures. Items may arrive in a week or as long as 3 to 4 weeks. We have absolutely no control over postal costs and time of delivery. Thanks for your patience. Payment Instructions: We welcome international buyers but you must pay by PayPal with a credit card or direct deposit. Payments must be made within 72 hours of auction end.
